    <learningContentbody>
        <lcInstruction>
            <p>The &lt;note> element lets you create notes, cautions, warnings, and other
                admonishments. The type attribute for the &lt;note> element allows you to indicate
                different kinds of notes. DITA defines a number of values for the type attribute:<ul
                    id="ul_irt_jdr_bs">
                    <li>note (the default)</li>
                    <li>attention</li>
                    <li>danger</li>
                    <li>caution</li>
                    <li>important</li>
                    <li>tip</li>
                    <li>and more</li>
                </ul></p>
        </lcInstruction>
    </learningContentbody>
